# Reasoning Lessons

**Reference:** DSM_0.2 Reasoning Lessons Protocol
**Pruning cadence:** Every 5 sessions (next: Session {N})
**File size target:** ~70 entry lines (excluding headers and comments), maximum 200 lines hard cap
**Last pruned:** _(none yet)_

## Tagging Convention

- `[auto]` , extracted by CA at wrap-up (lightweight, automated)
- `[STAA]` , extracted by STAA in dedicated analysis session (full analysis)

## Categories

### Decision Heuristics

_Lessons about when to apply a rule or how to choose between alternatives._

### Ecosystem Patterns

_Lessons about how this project interacts with DSM Central and other spokes._

### Infrastructure

_Lessons about tooling, hooks, skills, settings, and the agent's working environment._

### Methodology

_Lessons about protocol effectiveness, gaps, or boundary conditions._

### Skills

_Lessons about slash-command behavior, edge cases, and skill authoring._

